WEBVTT

00:00.070 --> 00:01.808
<i>ALEXANDER: Previously</i>
<i>on The Borgias...</i>

00:01.890 --> 00:03.562
<i>ALEXANDER:</i>
<i>We are in a snake pit</i>

00:03.664 --> 00:05.629
<i>surrounded by venom.</i>

00:05.697 --> 00:08.100
<i>We shall cleanse the</i>
<i>College of Cardinals.</i>

00:08.167 --> 00:09.835
<i>CATHERINA SFORZA:</i>
<i>Vitelli, Orsini.</i>

00:09.908 --> 00:11.379
Let us gather them to us.

00:11.447 --> 00:13.049
RUFIO: Catherina Sforza
invites you all

00:13.117 --> 00:15.388
to join her in a
confederacy of hatred.

00:15.456 --> 00:17.629
Until the Borgia
snake is lanced.

00:17.697 --> 00:19.636
CESARE: Catherina Sforza
seeks out allies.

00:19.704 --> 00:22.045
ALEXANDER:
Give her a lesson in revenge.

00:22.113 --> 00:23.481
<i>CARDINAL SFORZA: There was</i>
<i>a plot to rid the Earth</i>

00:23.549 --> 00:24.783
<i>of the Borgia family.</i>

00:24.851 --> 00:26.785
So tell me, what must I do?
Confess.

00:26.853 --> 00:28.992
To a crime I would never
even dream of committing!

00:29.060 --> 00:30.594
Then name those who would.

00:30.661 --> 00:32.195
<i>DE LUCA:</i>
<i>Cardinal Sforza!</i>

00:32.262 --> 00:34.665
ALFONSO: My uncle has
expressed his disquiet

00:34.733 --> 00:37.438
at the thought of a child
without legitimacy.

00:37.506 --> 00:39.373
You are to negotiate
my dowry, Brother.

00:39.441 --> 00:41.209
If Naples dares to
take your son from you,

00:41.277 --> 00:42.744
it will never know
peace again.

00:42.812 --> 00:44.746
My betrothed will
not bed me.

00:44.814 --> 00:46.214
He is a virgin.

00:46.282 --> 00:49.085
<i>I am a Borgia.</i>
<i>I feel unloved.</i>

00:49.153 --> 00:50.487
[knocking]
My lady.

00:51.790 --> 00:53.124
Why am I here?

00:53.192 --> 00:55.395
To learn to lie.
To say whatever's needed.

00:55.462 --> 00:57.832
Cardinal Francesco
Todeschini Piccolomini.

00:57.899 --> 01:00.736
Liar!
Cardinal Giovanni Battista Orsini.

01:00.803 --> 01:02.637
These are false
accusations coming from-

01:02.705 --> 01:05.038
Cardinal Rocca Colonna!
Julius Versucci!

01:05.105 --> 01:07.674
I have been party to
no conspiracy, Your Holiness!

01:07.742 --> 01:09.009
ALEXANDER:
Those cardinals

01:09.077 --> 01:11.211
will be stripped
of their offices and titles.

01:11.279 --> 01:13.848
They will be forbidden entry
through the gates of Rome.

01:13.916 --> 01:15.184
ORSINI:
My sins are many.

01:15.251 --> 01:17.853
But the greatest of them
is this murder.

01:19.390 --> 01:23.560
[grunting and struggling]

01:26.598 --> 01:28.333
ALEXANDER:
God must want us to live.

01:30.234 --> 01:33.363
[♪]

01:33.364 --> 01:37.364
<font color=#00FF00>♪ The Borgias 3x03 ♪ </font>
